platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.ta.k: 首首原創歌曲，陪青春樂隊追夢
組成青春樂團 敲響音樂節奏
青春物語を描いた音楽ゲーム

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: If you like rhythm games, you’ve got to check out Voez. You tap, swipe and press to the beat—all while the tracks are swirling around the screen, fantastic music is blasting and colours burst in every direction. It’s as awesome as it sounds.
